page.title: 19LAINDON'S FAMOUS PEOPLE
page.content: {Alison Moyet}_ from Laindon aged 25. Originally a member of{Yazoo,}now sings solo. Latest song "That Old Devil Called Love." {Cheryl Baker}from Basildon aged 27. A member of pop group{"Bucks Fizz." { Dave Gahn -}Laindon. A member pop group{"Depeche Mode." {Joan Sims -}born in Laindon. She is an actress who has appeared in many {"Carry On"}films. Her first appearance was at the{Radion Cinema}in Laindon. The Radion Cinema, however, was pulled down when Laindon became part of {Basildon New Town.
